phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common WorkManager mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Heavy work on main | Use coroutines |
| No retry | Use Result.retry() |
| No progress | Use setProgress |
| No constraints | Set constraints |
| No input/output | Use inputData/outputData |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Use coroutines
override suspend fun doWork(): Result {
    delay(5000) // Non-blocking
    return Result.success()
}

// 2. Add retry
catch (e: Exception) {
    Result.retry()
}

// 3. Report progress
setProgress(workDataOf("progress" to 50))

// 4. Set constraints
Constraints.Builder()
    .setRequiredNetworkType(NetworkType.CONNECTED)
    .build()

// 5. Use input/output
val url = inputData.getString("url")
val output = workDataOf("result" to "done")
```
